Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾发生过战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后被称为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“极光战争”的这场战乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生在赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.80,0:00:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和茵费利亚之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.61,0:00:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赛雷斯提亚便断绝交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.61,0:00:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.35,0:00:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.98,0:00:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个世界面临即将灭亡的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出来拯救这场危机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是一群无名的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.99,0:02:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临贝鲁卡纽餐厅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.36,0:02:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是贝鲁卡椰苏打水的试饮会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.83,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是演戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.04,0:02:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打输对我来说也是很没面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是装个样子有什么关系嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.71,0:02:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你   温蒂妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是被你们打败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.85,0:02:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真是乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.15,0:02:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过非常谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.89,0:02:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6话  贝鲁卡纽之迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.94,0:02:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把这心中的激动写成一首诗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.71,0:02:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船终于完成了   好高兴哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家的帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.55,0:02:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有玛萝妮也是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…因为没事做，所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可以继续旅行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再使点劲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.43,0:03:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.80,0:03:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有浮起来  有浮起来耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我们成功了哟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常成功！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.54,0:03:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想想看是谁设计的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遇上了暴风雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.61,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能沉下去的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你看那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.89,0:03:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉下去了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太勉强自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是您有个什么万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.65,0:04:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么成呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那些家伙暂时也出不了海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您还是去休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.59,0:04:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在这里稍后一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会愿意把船借我们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没其他办法了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且我们也没有钱再重新造船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人愿意接见你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思以这个模样见你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我实在有太多事要忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.06,0:05:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.22,0:05:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照那样子就算拉的上来也不能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是你设计上有问题啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的设计非常完美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们没有照设计图作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在海底捡到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是晶灵语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶灵语？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是过去晶灵文明全盛的时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所使用的一种语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在茵费利亚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是拿来当晶灵的咒文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是在学术文献里有记载而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.76,0:05:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过赛雷斯提亚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.00,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今好像也很普遍在使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像梅露蒂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不也是只会说晶灵语吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.81,0:06:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多亏有公主的耳环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才有办法跟我们沟通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  经你这么一提…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这实在是太罕见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.75,0:06:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是晶灵时代的货币啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为这里的领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须优先考虑岛上的重建工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能为了你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就特别把船出借给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.27,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.34,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.91,0:06:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不   没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.04,0:06:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉对您提出这么任性的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们会停留在这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许也是圣法特神的旨意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.15,0:06:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何不暂时让自己放松一下呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有海水的味道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我刚刚掉到海里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.13,0:07:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…要不要下来一起泡澡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由…日出之方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.67,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日…落之方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么意思啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.04,0:07:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我曾看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不少晶灵时代的货币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种的还是头一次见到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是有其他的用途也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.29,0:07:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家说要以岛的重建工作为优先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为领主  这是必然的判断啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有祈祷驶往大陆的定期船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.10,0:07:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够尽快重新复航啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.77,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只为这点小事就受挫的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.97,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拯救不了赛雷斯提亚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  干脆去洗个澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切不愉快的事情都冲掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.48,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得这时候能不能洗澡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面好像有人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.09,0:08:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.99,0:08:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思让你们撞见这个窘状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我们已经先进来洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的温度怎么样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.90,0:08:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.96,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为又重新加入了入浴剂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就听普拉提亚小姐的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.17,0:08:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来一起浸浴  可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂好像有点故障的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水温一直热不起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是之前发现到的石塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好这岛上出乎意外的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有许多晶灵文明的遗迹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来拿这个而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便的话  两位请…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  你觉得这里怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就决定这里了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.74,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉  温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且全身都是鹹水味也蛮讨厌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你们来的正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观光指南啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去泡温泉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.82,0:09:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快的温泉真令人期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要一起去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.13,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~这主意不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.13,0:09:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德和基尔怎么可以去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然是开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.17,0:09:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们这群女生去洗温泉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.51,0:09:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还真悠哉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.74,0:09:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张地图…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面并没有画出那座石塔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是忘了画啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规模那么大的一座石塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会是重要的观光胜地才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…是故意不把他画出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.82,0:09:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到在石塔的背面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏有这么一座废弃的城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会不会想太多了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是普通的废墟而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为应该不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟晶灵文明有什么关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.52,0:10:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里到完全没人居住为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概也不过一百年前左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔你要不要紧哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉就在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  基尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了啦  基尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  他到底是怎么搞的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.14,0:11:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜的果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭坛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被之前的台风弄坏了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.49,0:11:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千辛万苦好不容易到达的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却找不到…温泉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我们特地到这里来的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.14,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们往这边走走看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那水蛮烫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想也只剩那里了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是地图上画的只有这里而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里算是不为人知的温泉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正跟我走就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往这边走会有什么东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没发现到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.76,0:12:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个城镇的祭坛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是朝同一个方向摆设
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定代表了什么意思才对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这边对吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.44,0:12:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有听到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.48,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必喊那么多次啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔你快点过来看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上一个人的优劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是靠体力来决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你有没有听到我说话啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.46,0:12:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错  是晶灵文明的遗迹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要进去看看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.44,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当然！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上存在了这样的遗迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信当地居民绝不可能会不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是地图上居然没标示出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  现在还没…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像没路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.89,0:13:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有移动过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如另一边还有通路的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成墙上有什么机关吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.64,0:13:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.95,0:13:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.52,0:13:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没发生耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西的大小跟那一模一样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.77,0:13:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由日出之方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.47,0:13:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到日落之方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.44,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.68,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由日出之方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.15,0:14:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到日落之方！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神殿的回廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是怎么进来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能放他们到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.94,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂脚已经酸了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.45,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的有温泉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂先浸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.57,0:15:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这水好烫哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你突然跳进去的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  这样就能调整温度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.08,0:15:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  其实没有很热嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.62,0:15:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点温度忍耐一下的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有办法泡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来玛萝妮怕泡很烫的水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪有啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.84,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.15,0:15:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说得也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐得我不知不觉想跳起舞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要在那里搅热水啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.75,0:15:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不可以呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.86,0:15:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为真正的泡澡是要静静的泡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就泡到肩膀的高度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  泡到肩膀的话这对身体…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.90,0:16:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样身体内部整个都热起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.48,0:16:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经走到下面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.61,0:16:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近可能有地下水脉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来玛萝妮还是有弱点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰唆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是来干嘛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为梅露蒂也很怕烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边  这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.01,0:16:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.34,0:16:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮  我们是朋友对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当你是朋友才坦白告诉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实梅露蒂他…是赛雷斯提亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.86,0:17:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不笑我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我只要这么说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分都会被瞧不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还被大家嘲笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我笑你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你这么轻易就相信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.81,0:17:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以前的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就会认为你在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.62,0:17:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚人啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚人好像很怕烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有对料理的味道也很挑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.96,0:17:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后额头上那个像玻璃珠的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来像是头饰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.93,0:17:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那叫做艾拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.97,0:17:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是赛雷斯提亚人特有的器官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么东西在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么怪物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.77,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从来没看过啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.21,0:18:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎牙破斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊弗力特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是火属性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量派不上用场！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就用风之晶灵术…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.11,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.95,0:19:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近可能有地下水脉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.19,0:19:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裂空斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.28,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.87,0:20:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…奇怪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.44,0:20:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧神殿的回廊似乎已完全封闭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.78,0:20:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的计划达成之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能让任何人来破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们像赛雷斯提亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报完仇之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待下回…精彩好戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很唐突  不过我是黑豹·约翰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如上所述  我是黑玫瑰·米莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而本大爷就是黑龙王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.80,0:21:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…已经没时间了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.76,0:21:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回   漆黑之翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你们是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.40,0:21:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细听好…


